items.title: The Warriors
items.headline: Welcome to the Warriors Wiki!
items.desc: The Warriors is a 1979 American cult action/thriller film directed by Walter Hill and based on Sol Yurick's 1965 novel of the same name. Like the novel, the film borrows elements from the Anabasis by Xenophon.

items.name: Bravest Warriors Wiki
items.title: Bravest Warriors Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Bravest Warriors Wiki!
items.desc:
The Bravest Warriors Wiki is an unofficial collaborative database about the animated series, Bravest Warriors, that anyone can contribute to.

Bravest Warriors is an animated series created by Pendleton Ward and produced by Frederator Studios for their Cartoon Hangover YouTube channel. The series is about four teenage heroes-for-hire: Chris, Beth, Danny and Wallow.

It premiered in November 8, 2012, before the release of the Bravest Warriors comic. Unlike other cartoons, Bravest Warriors will be exclusively available on Cartoon Hangover's YouTube channel. This means that the series will not be shown on television like most media.

items.name: Bravest Warriors Wiki
items.title: Bravest Warriors Wiki
items.headline: Bienvenido a Bravest Warriors Wiki en Español
items.desc:
Bravest Warriors Wiki es una base de datos de colaboración no oficial sobre la serie animada Bravest Warriors, en la que cualquiera puede contribuir.

Bravest Warriors es una serie creada por Pendleton Ward (el creador de Hora de Aventura) y Frederator Studios.
El piloto fue lanzado el 10 de enero de 2009 en Random! Cartoons.

La serie trata sobre 4 adolescentes llamados Chris, Beth, Danny y Wallow, los cuales forman un equipo llamado Bravest Warriors (el cual le da nombre a la serie) que salva el Universo.

items.name: Bravest Warriors Wiki
items.title: Bravest Warriors Wiki
items.headline: Przyjżyj się bliżej Bravest Warriors Wiki!
items.desc: Bravest Warriors Wiki jest jedyną polskojęzyczną Wiki o serialu animowanym Bravest Warriors. Codziennie dokładamy wszelkich informacji, starań oraz poprawek by strony były jak najbardziej dopracowane ale jednocześnie proste w odbiorze. Każdy szczeguł i pomoc się tu przyda więc rozejrzyj się i dołącz do najdzielniejszych bohaterów!

items.name: World of Warriors Wiki
items.title: World of Warriors Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the World of Warriors Wiki!
items.desc:
World of Warriors is a mobile adventure and combat strategy game developed by Mind Candy and released November 11th, 2014. Warriors blends fighting and RPG gameplay and features an ever-expanding array of the greatest warriors in history, from Ninjas and Aztecs to Knights and Vikings. Every warrior comes with their own backstory, special moves and historical facts. World of Warriors is currently available for the iOS platform and it is free to play.

This wiki is designed and edited by the fans of World of Warriors. Anyone can contribute and are encouraged to do so. If you need help with an article, please feel free to leave a message on the talk wall of the Admins. You might even find someone in the chat room. Come join us!

items.title: WeAreWarriors Wikia
items.desc: Are you obsessed with Erin Hunter's bestselling series Warriors? Do you dream of roleplaying your very own Warrior cat with their story? This site lets you live the dream of becoming one! You get to create as many cats as you can handle, chat with friends, go to gatherings, and maybe even become the leader of a clan!
